org.datavec.api.records.reader

Interface SequenceRecordReader

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable, java.io.Closeable, Configurable, RecordReader, java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseCodecRecordReader, CodecRecordReader, CollectionSequenceRecordReader, CSVNLinesSequenceRecordReader, CSVSequenceRecordReader, InMemorySequenceRecordReader, NativeCodecRecordReader, RegexSequenceRecordReader, TransformProcessSequenceRecordReader, VideoRecordReader

    public interface SequenceRecordReader
extends RecordReader
    A sequence of records. sequenceRecord() is used locally. sequenceRecord(URI uri, DataInputStream dataInputStream) is used for spark etc.
